     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet KomplikationerDKRR</b></p><a name=\"KomplikationerDKRR\"> </a><a name=\"hcKomplikationerDKRR\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/Complications</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html#Complications-infection\">infection</a></td><td>Infektion</td><td>Sårinfektion</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html#Complications-dvt\">dvt</a></td><td>DVT</td><td>Dyb vene trombose</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html#Complications-movement_restriction\">movement_restriction</a></td><td>Bevægeindskrænkning(&gt; 5 graders ext., &gt; 10 graders fleksion indskrækning)</td><td>Movement restriction / Bevægelsesindskrænkning</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html#Complications-chronic_pain\">chronic_pain</a></td><td>Kronisk smerter</td><td>Chronic pain / Kronisk smerte</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html#Complications-reoperation\">reoperation</a></td><td>Reoperation</td><td>Reoperation</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/GenericValues</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html#GenericValues-other\">other</a></td><td>Anden komplikation</td><td>Other - used to choose unspecific value not in a valueset</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
